-- Arpe, Partners Plan Offer for Fondiaria-Sai, Repubblica Says
-- B y   L o r e n z o   T o t a r o
-- 2012-04-28T08:19:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-28/arpe-partners-plan-offer-for-fondiaria-sai-repubblica-says.html
Matteo Arpe’s private-equity firm
and its partner plan an offer for  Fondiaria-Sai SpA (FSA)  after
 Italy ’s competition authority suspended the insurer’s merger
with  Unipol Gruppo Finanziario SpA (UNI) , la Repubblica reported
without saying where it got the information.  According to the plan, Arpe’s Sator Capital Ltd. and
Palladio Finanziaria SpA would support half of the 800 million
euros ($1.06 billion) capital increase Fondiaria-Sai needs to
return to profit, the Rome-based newspaper said. The other half
would be raised on the market, la Repubblica reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at 
 cstirling1@bloomberg.net  